Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,40,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,手都僵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我很怕冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,暖宝宝要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好大一片冰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想拿回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都不是小学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,西片呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 比什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,到校门为止 拿的冰块大就算赢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是掉到地上就算输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你先来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿了大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能撑到校门口就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,高木同学着急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我不可能弄掉这冰块的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我从小看到冰块一定会带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,手指习惯了寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说我不可能手僵住放开冰块的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,加上 对每天做高木同学捉弄我次数三倍俯卧撑的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这点冰块一点都不重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让你后悔跟我挑起这场胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,高木同学 今天就要输给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉西片就像是拿着大块冰高兴的小学生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,失策了 「弄掉它」原来是这种做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今天一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,捏那么紧会碎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,担心敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那么从容呢 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不过的确 太用力会碎的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 作为惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,输的人要给赢的暖手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,掌握了 这样的力道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说呢 输的人要给赢的暖手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,笑过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你好弱啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说要给赢的人暖手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不能其他的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给我暖宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,早 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你一脸想好比什么的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一脸我说中的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那比什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 今天我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那 我和昨天哪里不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是心情什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是外观
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看不出来吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其实昨天晚上稍微剪了一点头发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点犯规 不如说是卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是赢就是赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我再观察观察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我忍不住自己说出来吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有地方不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 没有把被盯着看算进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为在衣服里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 看得见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,反应太大了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,中途被这样捉弄也没算进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往的弱呢 侧腹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是想这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为是眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,脸很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说不一样的是脸红的程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,味道怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说是外观了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说高木同学其实是知道答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了捉弄我玩而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这完全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有计算在内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难为情的话放弃也没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,故意让我放弃 就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,自己不知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说熬过现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,答案呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是头发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻能改变的外观 也就指甲跟头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是指甲就是头发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那作为惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我也改变一下外观
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来你来猜咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我难为情不敢盯着看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被反过来搞 也没算进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,冷起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你这头发怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天自己剪了下就
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,剪多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以叫你别笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是刘海像是搞坏了一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,搞坏掉一样的刘海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我还挺中意的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 美奈 有点说过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很合适你的 这刘海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是 朋友的话应该好好鼓励的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我却一直在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 友加里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是2月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,西片 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,平常心 平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,西片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有体育课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说里面有谁给的巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才打开鞋箱有点失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是情人节 我也没有期待什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 不如说就因为这个时候才会来捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,橡皮借我下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我橡皮的时候 自然地给我巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样讲的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很搞笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么给出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 今天是情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,做了好多巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,想要的人来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 爱的自制巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,女子力好高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样传播爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好好发吧 日比野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会去拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是性格跟美奈那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力发现就没收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说过的吧 日比野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦 还要注意老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能送出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太过分了 都没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太惨了 这样到处散播爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,问问送出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要说送的话已经送出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么送的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,高木也难为情的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我想亲手送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何也要 这样也能表达心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就像是试炼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就在海边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 中井君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就是试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,跨越这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就会更加紧密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 中井
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,女朋友送你巧克力了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么生气了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行 绝对做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总是跟男生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我要送巧克力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,机灵一点一个人行动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有想要我的巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,突然跑了 就追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你生什么气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,借出去的书 还给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,书的话就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,迟钝迟钝迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉 心力交瘁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,日比野的巧克力 早知道就去拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个没法收啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要北条同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,西片反正有高木同学给的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,走咯 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,结果什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还好 还给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有期待什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,情人节没有被捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天大胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是木村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是木村的恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道是谁放的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在应该就在身边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉 是高木同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可是万一不是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,知道今天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,回答正确
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那给你巧克力咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,给我巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说这不是高木同学给的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,义理的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那这边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这巧克力知道是谁给的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道也没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,紫式部的源氏物语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,清少纳言的枕草子也作为的研究对象
